  <brief_title>Feasibility of the Modified Confusion Assessment Method for the Emergency Department (mCAM-ED)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study on the Feasibility of the Modified Confusion Assessment Method for the Emergency Department (mCAM-ED)</official_title>
